OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774576986
OL,3,CStarmer: Trump criticism is to
OL,4,Cpressure me on Iran but I won't buckle
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has suggested Donald
OL,7,FTrump's criticism of him is an attempt
OL,8,Fto push him to change his stance on
OL,9,Fthe Iran war but vowed not to "buckle"
OL,10,Funder the pressure.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister said he had "core
OL,13,Fvalues and principles" that were
OL,14,F"irreducible" and would not waver on
OL,15,Fhis insistence that Britain will not
OL,16,Fbe dragged into the "wider" conflict
OL,17,Fbeyond defensive action.
OL,26,@qD@_OUqD@fO]tD@`OUuD@VO]vD@AOUvD@MO]xD@
OL,26,AUOUxD@[O]
