PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774576986
OL,3,CStarmer: Trump criticism is to
OL,4,Cpressure me on Iran but I won't buckle
OL,6,FIt comes after the US President
OL,7,Flaunched a fresh tirade against the UK
OL,8,Ffor the extent of its involvement in
OL,9,Fthe Middle East, saying Sir Keir made
OL,10,F"a big mistake" and denigrating
OL,11,FBritish warships as "toys".
OL,13,FAsked whether Mr Trump's repeated
OL,14,Fattacks had made him bristle, the
OL,15,FPrime Minister told Sky News'
OL,16,FElectoral Dysfunction podcast: "I
OL,17,Fthink I understand what's happening,
OL,18,Fit's to put pressure on me in
OL,19,Fdifferent ways.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@OO]sD@UOUsD@ZO]xD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774576986
OL,3,CStarmer: Trump criticism is to
OL,4,Cpressure me on Iran but I won't buckle
OL,6,F"But, that pressure isn't going to
OL,7,Fmake me waver. It's not going to make
OL,8,Fme abandon my principles or values,
OL,9,Fand that's just the way I am.
OL,11,F"That is not new. That isn't because
OL,12,Fof President Trump. I've got core
OL,13,Fvalues and principles I've held all my
OL,14,Flife, and they're irreducible."
OL,16,FHe acknowledged there was "a clear
OL,17,Fdifference of opinion" between himself
OL,18,Fand the president and that there had
OL,19,Fbeen "hard decisions" over recent
OL,20,Fweeks, but insisted he still wanted a
OL,21,F"good relationship".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@_O]xD@[OUyD@VO]{D@FOU{D@
OL,26,AUO]}D@AOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774576986
OL,3,CStarmer: Trump criticism is to
OL,4,Cpressure me on Iran but I won't buckle
OL,6,F"My own view is that a lot of what is
OL,7,Fsaid and done has been to put pressure
OL,8,Fon me to change my mind, but I'm not
OL,9,Fgoing to do so, because I'm the
OL,10,FBritish Prime Minister and I have to
OL,11,Fact in the British national interest,
OL,12,Fand I will always act in the British
OL,13,Fnational interest," Sir Keir said.
OL,15,FSpeaking at a televised White House
OL,16,FCabinet meeting earlier on Thursday,
OL,17,FMr Trump lashed out again at Nato for
OL,18,Fdoing "absolutely nothing" to help the
OL,19,FUS in the Middle East conflict.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@SO]zD@GOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774576986
OL,3,CStarmer: Trump criticism is to
OL,4,Cpressure me on Iran but I won't buckle
OL,6,FAnd he took aim at the UK's aircraft
OL,7,Fcarriers, HMS Queen Elizabeth and HMS
OL,8,FPrince of Wales.
OL,10,FHe said: "Now they all want to help.
OL,11,FWhen they're annihilated, the other
OL,12,Fside is annihilated, they said, 'we'd
OL,13,Flove to send ships'...
OL,15,F"We had the UK say that 'we'll send' `
OL,16,Fthis is three weeks ago ` 'we'll send
OL,17,Four aircraft carriers', which aren't
OL,18,Fthe best aircraft carriers, by the
OL,19,Fway. They're toys compared to what we
OL,20,Fhave."
OL,26,@rD@JOUwD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
