CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774576986
OL,3,CStarmer: Trump criticism is to
OL,4,Cpressure me on Iran but I won't buckle
OL,6,FMeanwhile, US defence secretary Pete
OL,7,FHegseth suggested that Iran has the
OL,8,Fcapability to strike London and
OL,9,Finsisted the president "knows better"
OL,10,Fthan others about the threat posed by
OL,11,FTehran.
OL,13,FEarlier, his British counterpart, John
OL,14,FHealey, refused to say if Iran was
OL,15,Fable to hit the UK, but said military
OL,16,Fchiefs did not believe the country had
OL,17,Fany plans to do so.
OL,26,@qD@XOUqD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
