OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774576986
OL,3,CStarmer: Trump criticism is to
OL,4,Cpressure me on Iran but I won't buckle
OL,6,FAsked whether he was angered by the US
OL,7,FPresident's action as the war
OL,8,Fjeopardises his promise earlier this
OL,9,Fyear to ease the cost of living for
OL,10,FBritons, Sir Keir said: "Of course,
OL,11,Fthere's a frustration there."
OL,13,FAsked whether he sometimes privately
OL,14,Fswore to himself about it, he said:
OL,15,F"Well, occasionally. I keep my
OL,16,Fexpletives to myself most of the time.
OL,17,FAlthough I don't think that's even
OL,18,Fsafe all the time.
OL,26,@rD@YOUsD@]O]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774576986
OL,3,CStarmer: Trump criticism is to
OL,4,Cpressure me on Iran but I won't buckle
OL,6,F"But look, I think if you're the
OL,7,FBritish Prime Minister, it's really
OL,8,Fimportant that we approach this with
OL,9,Four interests in mind and asking the
OL,10,Fquestion, how do we come out of this
OL,11,Fbetter, what are the conditions when
OL,12,Fwe went in, how do we come out of this
OL,13,Fbetter? And, these are the challenges
OL,14,Fof our time."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@MO]
